  "original_title": "\u0ba8\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc6\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bae\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb5\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba8\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bcb\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b85\u0bae\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bae\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Unrest over cooking gas supply in Nuwara Eliya",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "After last Thursday (14) in the main town of Nuwara Eliya, there was unrest among the people standing in queues and sales agents for two days after the announcement that LPG cylinders would be dispatched today by Litro LPG Company.",
        "After the sales agent announced today that cooking gas cylinders will be given on coupon mode, there was unrest between the people who were waiting in queues without coupons and the sales agents.",
        "However, with the intervention of the Nuwara Eliya Police, the situation was brought under control and they took steps to distribute cooking gas cylinders amid the security of the police, announcing that the remaining 20 people who were waiting in line and could not get it would be distributed in the form of coupons."
      ],
